[SHORT DESC]
User loses 50% max HP. Maximizes Atk.

[LONG DESC]
<h2>Description</h2>
<p>Costs the user 50% of its max HP, but brings Attack to +6 stages. In Gold and Silver, if the user uses Belly Drum when its HP is below 50%, it faints. In Crystal and Pokemon Stadium 2, it fails if the user has 50% HP or less. In Link Battles in cartridge games, using Belly Drum below 50% HP will report a fail message, but it will raise the user's Attack by 2 stages.</p>